file.name: swagger.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Exercise tracker API
  version: v1
paths:
  "/v1/signup":
    post:
      summary: Creates an user
      tags:
      - Signup
      parameters: []
      responses:
        '201':
          description: New User registered in the database
          content: {}
        '422':
          description: invalid request
          content: {}
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                name:
                  type: string
                email:
                  type: string
                password:
                  type: string
                password_digest:
                  type: string
              required:
              - name
              - email
              - password
              - password_digest
  "/v1/login":
    post:
      summary: Used to login users
      tags:
      - Login
      parameters: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Logs in an user and creates a new token
          content: {}
        '401':
          description: invalid credentials
          content: {}
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                email:
                  type: string
                password:
                  type: string
              required:
              - email
              - password
  "/v1/exercises":
    get:
      summary: List all exercises
      tags:
      - Exercise
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Shows all exercises no authentication is needed
          content: {}
  "/v1/exercises/{id}":
    get:
      summary: List an specific exercise
      tags:
      - Exercise
      parameters:
      - name: id
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Shows an specific exercise no authentication is needed
          content: {}
        '401':
          description: invalid credentials
          content: {}
servers:
- url: http://localhost:3000
  variables:
    defaultHost:
      default: http://localhost:3000
